<dd><b>TD</b> =3D Touchdown passes</dd>
<dd><b>INT</b> =3D Interceptions</dd></dl>
<p>If the result of any calculation is greater than 2.375, it is set to 2.3=
75. If the result is a negative number, it is set to zero.
</p><p>Then, the above calculations are used to complete the passer rating:
</p><p><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class=
