</li></ul>
<p>Wide receiver <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Antwaan_Randle_El=
" title=3D"Antwaan Randle El">Antwaan Randle El</a>, with a passer rating o=
f 157.5 from 21 completed passes of a possible 26, has the highest career r=
ating of any non-QB with more than twenty attempts.<sup id=3D"cite_ref-rand=
le_el_passer_rating_17-0" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikiped=
ia.org/wiki/Passer_rating#cite_note-randle_el_passer_rating-17"><span class=
=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>17<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup>=
 As of 2025, 82 NFL quarterbacks have <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w=
iki/List_of_NFL_quarterbacks_who_have_posted_a_perfect_passer_rating" class=
=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"List of NFL quarterbacks who have posted a perfec=
t passer rating">completed a game with a perfect passer rating</a> of 158.3=
, and seven have done so multiple times. <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.or=
g/wiki/Lamar_Jackson" title=3D"Lamar Jackson">Lamar Jackson</a>, <a href=3D=
"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ben_Roethlisberger" title=3D"Ben Roethlisber=
ger">Ben Roethlisberger</a>, and <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/P=
eyton_Manning" title=3D"Peyton Manning">Peyton Manning</a> are tied for the=
 record for the most games with a perfect passer rating, with four each. <a=
 href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Phil_Simms" title=3D"Phil Simms">Phi=
l Simms</a> holds the record for the highest passer rating in a Super Bowl,=
 at 150.92 in <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Super_Bowl_XXI" titl=
e=3D"Super Bowl XXI">Super Bowl XXI</a>.
</p>
